---
import Image from "../components/Image.astro";
import Layout from "../layouts/Page.astro";
---

<!doctype html>
<Layout
  title={null}
  description="Isiah Fletcher: Professional session drummer and React/TypeScript software engineer. Specializing in web development, digital health solutions, and versatile music performance across rock, jazz, metal, and beyond. Based in Olympia, Washington."
>
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section id="hero-section" class="hero-section">
    <div class="teaser-image">
      <Image
        width={400}
        height={300}
        src="/drummer-bubs-transparent.png"
        alt="Silhouette mid-solo"
        credit="Designed by the lovely Shelbz Citrine"
      />
    </div>
    <div class="hero-text">
      <h1>I'm Isiah</h1>
      <h2>And here's what I offer:</h2>
      <hr />

      <h3>Heavy Before Light</h3>
      <p>
        The root must be felt before the flower blooms. I dig into what's
        difficult—the shadow work of your brand, the technical debt, the story
        you're afraid to tell—because that's where transformation lives.
      </p>
      <h3>Primal Over Perfect</h3>
      <p>
        Your website doesn't need more polish. Your copy doesn't need more
        synonyms for "innovative." What you need is someone who can strip away
        the performance and find what's actually true.
      </p>
      <h3>Communion, Not Transaction</h3>
      <p>
        Code is relationship. Writing is ritual. Every project is an invitation
        to see what emerges when we stop optimizing and start being with the
        work.
      </p>
      <p>
        I've spent five years building React interfaces for digital health. I've
        spent longer learning that every creative act—every beat, every
        function, every sentence—is a petition to be more fully human in a world
        that would prefer we weren't.
      </p>
      <p>
        Your project doesn't need polish. It needs someone who remembers what it
        feels like to almost not be here, and chose to stay anyway.
      </p>
      <p>
        I work with people and projects that remember: the goal isn't
        perfection. It's presence. It's creating something that lands in the
        body, not just the browser.
      </p>
      <p>If that's what you're after, let's talk.</p>
      <div class="hero-ctas">
        <a href="#session-work" class="btn">Let’s Talk Drums</a>
        <a href="#programming-portfolio" class="btn">Let’s Talk Code</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Session Work Section -->
  <section id="session-work" class="media-grid-section">
    <h2>Session Work</h2>
    <p>
      I lend my beats across genres—rock, jazz, funk, pop, metal, folk and
      beyond.
    </p>
    <div class="media-grid">
      <!-- replace VIDEO_ID_X below -->
      <iframe
        src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/lc_rCn2em8o?si=HdoxTRHM6UDSzZWV"
        title="Session Clip 1"
        allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture"
        allowfullscreen></iframe>
      <iframe
        src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/4MM4Ta2QIOI?si=2DKAmfy74pPOn2y8"
        title="Session Clip 2"
        allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture"
        allowfullscreen></iframe>
      <iframe
        src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/vNU7E_5oVJo?si=FeOtTYWNN6h-_AQx"
        title="Session Clip 3"
        allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture"
        allowfullscreen></iframe>
    </div>
    <a
      href="https://www.youtube.com/@isiahfletcher2859"
      class="btn"
      target="_blank"
      rel="noopener">Explore More on YouTube</a
    >
  </section>

  <!-- Programming Portfolio Section -->
  <section id="programming-portfolio" class="media-grid-section">
    <h2>Programming Portfolio</h2>
    <p>
      Four years in digital health tech at Hinge Health—crafting React JS
      interfaces and design systems.
    </p>
    <div class="card-grid">
      <a
        href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/isiah-fletcher-074060159/"
        class="card-link"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener"
      >
        <div class="card">
          <div class="card-thumb hinge-thumb"></div>
          <div class="card-content">
            <h3>Hinge Health</h3>
            <p>React JS · Storybook · TypeScript</p>
            <span class="btn small">View on LinkedIn</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </a>

      <a
        href="https://shelbzcitrine.com/"
        class="card-link"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener"
      >
        <div class="card">
          <div class="card-thumb shelbz-thumb"></div>
          <div class="card-content">
            <h3>Shelbz Citrine Portfolio</h3>
            <p>
              A vibrant showcase of Shelbz’s art and design, built with NextJS.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </a>
    </div>

    <!-- Core Values -->
    <section id="values" class="values">
      <div class="value">
        <h4>Relentless Curiosity</h4>
        <p>I pry open every tight seam—be it a groove or a graph.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="value">
        <h4>Fearless Creation</h4>
        <p>
          I chase wild ideas into daylight so you don’t lie awake wondering
          “what if?”
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="value">
        <h4>Unflinching Storytelling</h4>
        <p>Every beat, every line, every breath carries its own tale.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Final Pitch -->
    <section id="final-pitch" class="final-pitch">
      <h2>
        Your project demands more than routine. It yearns for a provocateur.
      </h2>
      <div class="final-ctas">
        <a href="/contact" class="btn">Drop Me a Line</a>
        <a href="/work" class="link">View Résumé</a>
      </div>
    </section>
  </section>

  <style>
    /* Hero Section */
    .hero-section {
      display: flex;
      gap: 2rem;
      flex-wrap: wrap-reverse;
      padding: 3rem 0;
      padding-top: 0;
    }
    .hero-section .teaser-image {
      flex: 1 1 300px;
    }
    .hero-section .teaser-image img {
      width: 100%;
      height: auto;
      max-width: 400px;
    }
    .hero-section .hero-text {
      flex: 2 1 400px;
    }
    .hero-ctas .btn {
      margin-right: 1rem;
    }

    /* Media Grid Sections */
    .media-grid-section {
      padding: 3rem 0;
    }
    .media-grid-section h2 {
      font-size: 2rem;
      margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    }
    .media-grid-section p {
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      line-height: 1.5;
    }
    .media-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(320px, 1fr));
      gap: 1rem;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }
    .media-grid iframe {
      width: 100%;
      aspect-ratio: 16/9;
      border: none;
    }
    .card-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
      gap: 1.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }
    .card {
      height: 100%;
      background: rgba(var(--gray-dark), 100%);
      border-radius: 8px;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .card-link {
      display: block;
      text-decoration: none;
      color: inherit;
      transition:
        transform 0.2s ease,
        box-shadow 0.2s ease;
    }

    .card-link:hover {
      transform: translateY(-6px);
      box-shadow:
        0px 10px 15px -3px var(--accent-dark),
        0px 4px 6px -2px var(--accent),
        0px 2px 4px var(--accent-dark);
    }
    .card-thumb {
      width: 100%;
      height: 250px;
      aspect-ratio: 16 / 9;
      background-size: contain;
      background-position: center;
      background-repeat: no-repeat;
      border-top-left-radius: 8px;
      border-top-right-radius: 8px;
    }

    .shelbz-thumb {
      background-image: url("/shelbzcitrine-thumb.jpg");
      /* fallback background color while image loads: */
      background-color: #f0e6d2;
    }
    .hinge-thumb {
      background-image: url("/hinge-health-thumb.jpeg");
    }
    .card-content {
      padding: 1rem;
    }
    .btn.small {
      padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
      font-size: 0.875rem;
    }

    /* Core Values */
    .values {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 2rem;
      padding: 3rem 0;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .value {
      flex: 0 0 30%;
    }

    @media (max-width: 720px) {
      .value {
        flex: 0 0 100%;
      }
    }
    .value h4 {
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }

    /* Final Pitch */
    .final-pitch {
      padding: 4rem 0;
      text-align: center;
      background: rgba(var(--gray-dark), 100%);
    }
    .final-pitch h2 {
      font-size: 2rem;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }
    .final-ctas .btn {
      margin-right: 1rem;
    }
    .link {
      color: #ffcc00;
      text-decoration: underline;
    }
  </style>
</Layout>
